OL,3,CWater boss admits bill rises could
OL,4,Cleave 100,000 customers struggling to
OL,5,Cpay
OL,7,FThe boss of South East Water has told
OL,8,FITV Meridian expected price increases
OL,9,Fcould leave 100,000 customers
OL,10,Fstruggling to pay bills.
OL,12,FIn an exclusive interview with
OL,13,FSangeeta Bhabra, CEO David Hinton,
OL,14,Fadmitted the 22% hike in bills could
OL,15,Fpush customers onto its social tariff.
OL,17,FThe price rises are needed to fund
OL,18,Fimprovements to South East Water's
OL,19,Fnetwork, which Mr Hinton says are
OL,20,Fneeded to get performance back to
OL,21,Fwhere it should be.
