OL,7,FThe supplier was in the top three
OL,8,Fsuppliers ranked by water regulator,
OL,9,FOfwat, until 2020. But in its most
OL,10,Frecent review it was told it needed to
OL,11,Freduce supply interruptions by 96%.
OL,13,FThe chief executive denied that its
OL,14,Frecent poor performance, which saw
OL,15,Fsome customers left without supplies
OL,16,Ffor days, was due to dividend payments.
OL,18,FWatch: Sangeeta Bhabra sits down with
OL,19,FSouth East Water CEO, David Hinton.
