OL,7,FMr Hinton insisted less than #4million
OL,8,Fwas being paid to shareholders each
OL,9,Fyear, with almost all the money being
OL,10,Fput into infrastructure.
OL,12,F"It hasn't left and gone to
OL,13,Fshareholders", he said. "It's almost
OL,14,Flike a mortgage being transferred to a
OL,15,Fmortgage.
OL,17,F"We've been paying dividends in the
OL,18,Flow single digits, #2, #3, #4 million
OL,19,Feach year, which represents less than
OL,20,F1% return for our shareholders.
