OL,7,F"So I want it to be really clear to
OL,8,Four customers that we're not, that
OL,9,Fit's not leaving the business, it's
OL,10,Fstill in the business and still
OL,11,Ffunding our infrastructure."
OL,13,FSouth East Water needs around
OL,14,F#1.9billion over the next five years
OL,15,Fto fund its improvements, which it
OL,16,Fwants to raise by upping customer
OL,17,Fbills.
