OL,7,FThe money would be used to upgrade
OL,8,Finfrastructure, stop leaks and make
OL,9,Fthe system 'more resilient to climate
OL,10,Fchange.'
OL,12,FMr Hinton also highlighted the
OL,13,Fincrease in demand for water in the
OL,14,FSouth East since the pandemic, due to
OL,15,Fa rise in home working.
OL,17,FThis is a factor, he says, on why
OL,18,Fcapacity increases are needed, which
OL,19,Fwill cost significant sums of money.
