OL,7,FData from South East Water shows an
OL,8,Fincrease in the amount of water used
OL,9,Fduring weekday daytimes, he said,
OL,10,Fwhilst suppliers like Thames Water
OL,11,Fhave seen a drop in big cities as
OL,12,Fpeople stay home.
OL,14,FHe denied that the current system was
OL,15,Funable to cope due to underinvestment.
OL,16,FThe bill rises, he said, are needed to
OL,17,Fget ahead of climate change and react
OL,18,Fto the change in demand.
