OL,7,F"We recognise that for some, that bill
OL,8,Fincrease will be difficult", he told
OL,9,FSangeeta. "And so we've increased our
OL,10,Fsocial support in terms of social
OL,11,Ftariffs and reduced bills for those
OL,12,Fthat really do struggle to pay for it.
OL,14,F"It's a really important part of our
OL,15,Fplan. We're looking to add at least
OL,16,F100,000 extra customers to that social
OL,17,Ftariff to try and help those who
OL,18,Freally do struggle to pay for it."
